Package gw.api.financials

Class CheckPayeeInfo

java.lang.Object
gw.api.financials.CheckPayeeInfo
public class CheckPayeeInfo extends Object
Parameter Object class to hold all the parameters for check payee creation. It handles parameter for primary payee and additional payees.
Author:
gchang
